name: Plate Dreams Story
description:
I played a lot of baseball as a kid, Little League, etc.  and not at all in high school because of poor grades.  I had to have a “C” 2.0 average.  Well, some of you know how that goes. Drop out.   And this is what it has come to - making short videos and writing poetry.  Welcome to the world.
